      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "id": "classes",
      "classes": "Index-page Index-page--has-image",
      "bg": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "bgImage": null,
      "minHeight": "0px",
      "padding": "0px",
      "textSample": "CLASSES HATHA YOGA Hatha Yoga connects the body and mind through the practice of asanas (physical postures) and pranayama (breathing exercises). Focus and attention will be on the precise alignment of the body to achieve balance both mentally and physically. BOOK A CLASS DYNAMIC ",
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "id": "about",
      "classes": "Index-page",
      "bg": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
      "bgImage": null,
      "minHeight": "0px",
      "padding": "0px",
      "textSample": "ABOUT I came to yoga as a way to challenge my then awful flexibility and quiet my restless mind and was instantly struck by the healing powers of this discipline. I was extremely fascinated by the beautiful postures some of my fellow yogis achieved and dreamt of being able to per",
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f4e6ca4d96a2e7c741e1dbe/1604482039701-5FXXOQTZNEB24HTXEZLR/online-dynamic-yoga-classes?format=500w",
          "alt": "online-dynamic-yoga-classes",
          "w": 480,
          "h": 720
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "id": "mission",
      "classes": "Index-page",
      "bg": "rgb(255, 255, 255)",
      "bgImage": null,
      "minHeight": "0px",
      "padding": "0px",
      "textSample": "My mission is to guide people in their journey, emphasising the fact that you don’t have to be super flexible or perfect to do yoga – with some small, positive changes you’ll be able to live a more mindful and present life. As an ex-competitive swimmer and run lover, I’ve always ",
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5f4e6ca4d96a2e7c741e1dbe/1599560220424-4JPIXB4AB9RT0GQLZILG/1Z1A0155.jpg?format=500w",
          "alt": "online-yoga-classes-with-Ludo",
          "w": 480,
          "h": 720
        }
      ]
    },
